      "raw": "G5 B^T G5 = G5 (G5 conj(b_16) G5)^T G5 = G5 G5^T conj(b_16)^T G5^T G5",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "where A = b_16, B = rho_minus(b_16) = G5 conj(b_16) G5",
      "session": "",
