      "raw": "= G5^2 conj(b_16)^T G5^2 = conj(b_16)^T = b_16^dag (the dagger!)",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "G5 B^T G5 = G5 (G5 conj(b_16) G5)^T G5 = G5 G5^T conj(b_16)^T G5^T G5",
